<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.187806>
    bibo:endPage "36" ;
    bibo:journal "Zootaxa" ;
    bibo:startPage "1" ;
    bibo:volume "2108" ;
    dc:creator "Machado, Angelo B. M." ;
    dc:date "2009" ;
    dc:title "Denticulobasis and Tuberculobasis, new genera close to Leptobasis, with description of ten new species (Odonata: Coenagrionidae)." ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.187813>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.187817>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.187807> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.187813>
    dc:description "FIGURES 25 – 34. Tuberculobasis, male thorax in dorsal and lateral view in T. arara, holotype (25, 26); T. costalimai, holotype (27, 28); T. guarani, holotype (29, 30); T. inversa, holotype (31, 32); T. williamsoni, holotype (33, 34)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/187813/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.187817>
    dc:description "FIGURES 57 – 65. Tuberculobasis, male appendages in dorsal, lateral, and posterior view: T. arara, holotype (57 – 59); T. costalimai, paratypes (60 – 62); T. guarani, holotype (64, 65), T. inversa holotype in dorsal (63), dorso-lateral (66), and lateral (68) views. T. inversa, Tefé, Amazonas State, in postero-lateral (68) view [66, 67 by R. W. Garrison]." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/187817/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.187807>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Denticulobasis garrisoni, paratype: penis with distal segment raised [by R. W. Garrison]." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/187807/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

